Welcome to spwdecompose.exe, the savegame decomposition tool.

Overview
--------

  The spwdecompose tool extracts and decompresses all section data of SP:WaW and
  winSPWW2 savegames, allowing easy inspection and modification.

  The currently known data items in the savegame sections are documented in the
  "SPWAW_records.doc" and "winSPWW2_records.doc" files.


Usage
-----

  Usage: spwdecompose.exe GAME DIR INDEX
  Where: GAME    game type
         DIR     path to savegame dir
         INDEX   index of savegame to decompose
  
  Supported game types:
      SPWAW       SPWaW
      WINSPWW2    winSPWW2
  
  The savegame is decomposed, in separate sections, in the current directory.


Examples
--------

  To decompose the SP:WaW savegame from slot number 42, into the current
  directory, do:

  c:\path\to\spwdecompose.exe SPWAW c:\path\to\spwaw\SAVE 42

  To decompose the winSPWW2 savegame from slot number 84, into the current
  directory, do:

  c:\path\to\spwdecompose.exe WINSPWW2 "c:\path\to\winspww2\Saved Games" 42
